<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.8.8">
<l>aṇiyār poḻilcū ḻaraṅka nakarappā</l>
<l>tuṇiyē ṉiṉini ṉaruḷal lateṉakku</l>
<l>maṇiyē maṇimā ṇikkamē matucūtā</l>
<l>paṇiyā yeṉakkuy yumvakai parañcōtī.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Father of the city of Araṅkam encircled by beautiful groves,</l>
<l>Now I do not strive for anything but your grace for me.</l>
<l>Jewel, my jeweled ruby, Madhusūdana,</l>
<l>Tell me a way that will save [me], supreme splendor.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
